**III. Karma — The 9th Layer**

| **Every action has a karma.** Physics: Every action has an equal and opposite reaction. (Newton's 3rd Law) Philosophy: What you sow, you reap. (Universal Law) Spirituality: Everything is being observed. Every deed is recorded. Biology: Living systems self-calibrate. (Homeostasis) |
